The paper discusses a natural language processing task of generating questions for reading comprehension, which falls under the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.NE). The paper also involves the use of language models and information retrieval techniques, which are relevant to the sub-category of information retrieval (cs.IR).
